Audiobooks - Librivox library
Privacy Policy
Your privacy is critically important to us.  Your data is your own.  We make no claims to it and will only use it according to the policies outlined below.
If you have questions about deleting or correcting your personal data please contact our
support team
.
Gathering of Personally-Identifying Information
Audiobooks - Librivox library (Audiobooks) builds up a library of your listened to books within the app, this is not transmitted outside of the app.
Audiobooks will read basic state information (for example current cellular status) about your device in order to make informed decisions about managing your downloads.  This information is not transmitted outside of the app.
Protection of Certain Personally-Identifying Information
No Personally-Identifying Information is transmitted to external locations when using Audiobooks.
Cookies
A cookie is a string of information that a website stores on a visitor's computer, and that the visitor's browser provides to the website each time the visitor returns. The Audiobooks website identify and track visitors, their usage of Audiobooks website, and their website access preferences. The Audiobooks website visitors who do not wish to have cookies placed on their computers should set their browsers to refuse cookies before using Audiobooks's websites.
Business Transfers
If Audiobooks, or substantially all of its assets, were acquired, or in the unlikely event that Audiobooks goes out of business or enters bankruptcy, user information would be one of the assets that is transferred or acquired by a third party. You acknowledge that such transfers may occur, and that any acquirer of Audiobooks may continue to use your personal information as set forth in this policy.
Privacy Policy Changes
Although most changes are likely to be minor, Audiobooks may change its Privacy Policy from time to time, and in Audiobooks's sole discretion. Audiobooks encourages visitors to frequently check this page for any changes to its Privacy Policy. Your continued use of this site after any change in this Privacy Policy will constitute your acceptance of such change.
